B

BasicGhostPlayer - Class in ghosts
A player that has roughly the behavior of the ghosts in the real Pac-Man game: - deterministic as a function of the entire state history - doesn't reverse direction (thus not deterministic conditioned only on current state) - doesn't always pursue Pac-Man - doesn't get stuck in loops - covers much of the board At any given point in time, it has some part of the board that it wants to be near.
